ABOUT

Brookham Construction brings quality craftsmanship and attention to detail to every project. Based in Salt Lake City, we specialize in residential remodeling with a focus on creating spaces that enhance how you live.

Our team combines technical expertise with clear communication and on-time delivery. Licensed and insured, we work closely with clients throughout the entire process, ensuring your vision becomes reality within budget and on schedule.
